dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Waupaca County, WI 2022
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2022 and includes the layers 'Waupaca_Roads_2022' and 'Waupaca_ROW_2022'. [Roads: This data represents the Waupaca County transportation network. A single line is used to represent the center of a road. All roads are geocoded with a address range.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://data2017-04-05t135915451z-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/]
